<dt>《玉楸药解》<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="doctor" object-id="16">黄元御</a></dt></p><p><dd>味甘，气平，入手阳明大肠、足厥阴肝经。止痢敷血，利水秘精。</dd></p><p><dd>鸡内金扶中燥土，治泄痢崩带，尿血便红，喉痹<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1645">乳蛾</a>，口疮<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1866">牙疳</a>，失溺遗精，酒积食宿，胃反<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1195">膈</a>噎，并消<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1327">痈</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1316">疽</a>发背。</dd>
